68930,"like":0,"dislike":22,"score":-22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T14:23:05.000Z","msg":"加工processed先係紅 eg午餐肉<br />\n正正常常豬雞牛魚都係白"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T14:28:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0806f04f875dd51d4698be51f7d9039118ec8855","tid":828940,"uid":122709,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"0e75f9d9e8fdb127a671677cf16e040c5d043d7e","tid":828940,"uid":156370,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T05:58:18.000Z","msg":"紅肉白肉唔係用動物種類分"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T14:28:46.000Z","msg":"香港癌症基金會指出所有哺乳動物的肉均為紅肉，例如：牛、豬、羊，而白肉的例子則為雞、鴨、鵝、魚和蝦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2de2d254c8cb40c114af6c14f207fed24e9afbad","tid":828940,"uid":71218,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0806f04f875dd51d4698be51f7d9039118ec8855","tid":828940,"uid":122709,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"0e75f9d9e8fdb127a671677cf16e040c5d043d7e","tid":828940,"uid":156370,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T05:58:18.000Z","msg":"紅肉白肉唔係用動物種類分"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T14:28:46.000Z","msg":"香港癌症基金會指出所有哺乳動物的肉均為紅肉，例如：牛、豬、羊，而白肉的例子則為雞、鴨、鵝、魚和蝦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T14:42:46.000Z","msg":"雞都有分紅白,雞胸係白,雞比係接近紅,而鴨鵝應該係紅<br />\n通過骨骼肌係紅,非大量運動需要通常係白"},{"pid":"8afc800f1a75a9e19aa802d4753e5add61114bc6","tid":828940,"uid":156370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T14:48:42.000Z","msg":"係睇肉嘅<br />\n肌紅蛋白數量"},{"pid":"c4d129796a1869091c60cd85c8ef1926e5b3a940","tid":828940,"uid":156370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T14:49:29.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20161110/55895380\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20161110%2F55895380&d=hLOWhBhG0hlTLctC6GWcNcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=5ce1d564\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20161110%2F55895380&h=79c8a66f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20161110/55895380</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n紅肉，白肉，紅肉，白肉，單憑顏色就分得出？禽鳥類一定是白肉，四腳行走的一定是紅肉？到底如何分辨？<br />\n「家營營養中心」營養師陳筠霖說，其實一種肉是紅肉還是白肉，取決於它的肌紅蛋白數量。肌紅蛋白，是一種帶氧蛋白，當它處於帶氧狀態時候，就會呈紅色。如果肉類中的肌紅蛋白數量較高，那款肉就是紅肉。一般來說就是，牛、豬、鴨、鵝、羊、鴕鳥肉等等。相反，肌紅蛋白數量較少，雞、魚、海鮮等等，就是白肉。<br />\n不過又不能一概而論，以雞為例，雞胸雞翼都是白肉，但雞脾的肌紅蛋白較高，是紅肉。又例如牛肉，牛仔肉是白肉，因為肌紅蛋白數量不多，但成年牛的肉就是紅肉了。<br />\n許多人說，白肉比紅肉健康，還甚麼有這樣的講法？雖然紅肉通常含較高飽和脂肪，但同時擁有較高的鐵質和鋅。另外，亦要看部位，例如豬柳是紅肉，但脂肪低膽固醇低。雞翼是白肉，但脂肪高膽固醇高，就不及豬柳健康了。<br />\n有人問，雞是白肉，雞的內臟呢？其實大部份內臟，都屬於紅肉，而且一般膽固醇較高，鐘意食豬潤麵的朋友，要小心了。"},{"pid":"cb7f23713f8a86dcc330ba698274888c383462a2","tid":828940,"uid":151557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T15:05:03.000Z","msg":"我依家除咗雞之外，任何肉類都唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c25e41729f1bac84b4e237cabd9634be6108c31","tid":828940,"uid":186628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50c72de8482cde7f4b0cd30b8dd23dfcde8b45c5","tid":828940,"uid":168930,"like":0,"dislike":22,"score":-22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T14:23:05.000Z","msg":"加工processed先係紅 eg午餐肉<br />\n正正常常豬雞牛魚都係白"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T05:59:07.000Z","msg":"除左on9都唔知可以用咩詞彙形容你"},{"pid":"bf3e620286fb6f1451622f91a9712865010f1819","tid":828940,"uid":150973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87093feb8b277eb66f44120b78ac2c9787c63b86","tid":828940,"uid":31559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T04:57:12.000Z","msg":"幾個月前開始試下戒食紅肉，即係哺乳類動物<br />\n身體唔見有咩明顯改變<br />\n但消化係好咗，痾出來既屎靚咗<br />\n有冇一樣戒食巴打分享下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T07:14:21.000Z","msg":"屎係咩色"}]}